  19 Oct 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> kdenlive-0.5.ebuild:
  adjust deps for 0.5 version that only works with mlt < 0.3

*kdenlive-0.7_beta1 (16 Oct 2008)

  16 Oct 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +kdenlive-0.7_beta1.ebuild:
  Version bump, thanks to Tomáš Chvátal and for the ebuild and
  jmbsvicetto for the help on the missing kdebase-data dep. Bug #241712.

  12 Jul 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> kdenlive-0.5.ebuild:
  Check for xml useflag on mlt, thanks to Flyser <hoacha@quantentunnel.de>,
  bug #225015.

  12 May 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +files/kdenlive-0.5-iec61883_automagic.patch, kdenlive-0.5.ebuild:
  Fix automagic on libiec61883 by Olivier Huber <oli.huber@gmail.com>, bug
  #220095

  12 May 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> -kdenlive-0.4.ebuild:
  remove old

  11 Apr 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  adopt it in video herd, better than maintainer-needed

  11 Apr 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +files/kdenlive-0.5-gcc-4.3.patch, kdenlive-0.5.ebuild:
  gcc 4.3 build fix by Martin Väth <vaeth@mathematik.uni-wuerzburg.de>, bug
  #215720

  11 Apr 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +files/kdenlive-0.5-ffmpegheaders.patch, kdenlive-0.5.ebuild:
  Add a patch to let it build with latest ffmpeg headers layout

  10 Apr 2008; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> kdenlive-0.4.ebuild,
  kdenlive-0.5.ebuild:
  Go back to a sane versionning scheme for mlt++, bug #201492.

*kdenlive-0.5 (31 Mar 2008)

  31 Mar 2008; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org> +kdenlive-0.5.ebuild:
  Non-maintainer-bump (bug #188626), a lot of fixes and new features,
  including HD support. Thanks to Toffanin, Patrick Huber and Roberto
  Castagnola for contributions.
  
  This should also fix bug #193641.

  25 Dec 2007; Christian Heim <phreak@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Removing zypher from metadata.xml as per #26909. Assigning to
  maintainer-needed.

  22 Jul 2007; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>; kdenlive-0.4.ebuild:
  Drop virtual/x11 references.

  14 Apr 2007; Stefan Schweizer <genstef@gentoo.org> kdenlive-0.4.ebuild:
  Add built_with_use check thanks to Johannes Hirte <johannes-hirte@web.de> in
  bug 159812

